OL,3,CBoy, 9, died after being struck by
OL,4,Cfarm vehicle in tragic accident
OL,6,FA nine-year-old boy died after being
OL,7,Fstruck when his family attempted to
OL,8,Fjump from a runaway vehicle they
OL,9,Ffeared could fall off a cliff, an
OL,10,Finquest has heard.
OL,12,FTomos Rhys Bunford died from injuries
OL,13,Fto his chest and abdomen in an
OL,14,Fincident on farmland near Blaenllechau
OL,15,Fin the Rhondda, South Wales on
OL,16,FSeptember 6, 2021.
