OL,3,CBoy, 9, died after being struck by
OL,4,Cfarm vehicle in tragic accident
OL,6,FSouth Wales Central Coroner's Court
OL,7,Fheard that the young boy was in the
OL,8,Fback of his family's truck when it
OL,9,Fwent out of control and his father,
OL,10,FRhys Bunford, called for the family to
OL,11,Fjump from the vehicle, fearing it
OL,12,Fcould fall into a disused quarry.
OL,14,FAs they jumped, Tomos' mum, Louise
OL,15,FBunford, tried to push her son clear
OL,16,Fof the vehicle, which was towing a
OL,17,Fheavy water bowser on a trailer.
OL,19,FTomos was hit as the Mitsubishi
OL,20,FWarrior and the attached trailer jack-
OL,21,Fknifed down the slope.
