OL,3,CBoy, 9, died after being struck by
OL,4,Cfarm vehicle in tragic accident
OL,6,FTrack marks show the vehicle skidded
OL,7,Faround 86 metres down the incline.
OL,9,FAt an inquest on Tuesday, the
OL,10,Fcoroner's court heard the incident
OL,11,Fhappened as the family had been going
OL,12,Fto water their cows which lived on the
OL,13,Fland.
OL,15,FHis father spoke of how his son had
OL,16,Floved helping with his family farm,
OL,17,Foften telling classmates about feeding
OL,18,Fthe animals and he had a young calf he
OL,19,Fwalked around the yard on a lead.
