OL,3,CBoy, 9, died after being struck by
OL,4,Cfarm vehicle in tragic accident
OL,6,FMr Bunford told the coroner the trip
OL,7,Fwas something the family had done many
OL,8,Ftimes before, with older brother
OL,9,FGethin, mum Louise and baby Clemmie
OL,10,Falso in the truck.
OL,12,FHe was emotional as he told assistant
OL,13,Fcoroner Gavin Knox that as the vehicle
OL,14,Fhad started to go out of control he
OL,15,Ffeared it would fall off a "sheer
OL,16,Fdrop" into a disused quarry at the
OL,17,Fbottom of the slope.
OL,19,FMr Bunford said: "We all left to go
OL,20,Fover just like we did the week before.
