OL,6,F"We didn't do anything different from
OL,7,Fany other day, we went the same route
OL,8,Fdown an incline.
OL,10,F"As we were going down my son Gethin
OL,11,Fis in the passenger's seat, directly
OL,12,Fbehind me would be our young baby, my
OL,13,Fwife Louise would have been in the
OL,14,Fcentre and Tomos would have been to
OL,15,Fthe left.
OL,17,F"About halfway down the slope, it
OL,18,Fstarted to slip. There's a quarry (at
OL,19,Fthe bottom of the slope) and it's a
OL,20,Fsheer drop.
