OL,6,F"I thought it would be safer to exit
OL,7,Fthe vehicle than wait to see what
OL,8,Fhappens down there."
OL,10,FHe said as the vehicle began to pick
OL,11,Fup speed the bowser was jack-knifing,
OL,12,Fforcing the vehicle around 180 degrees.
OL,14,FMr Bunford said his initial fear was
OL,15,Ffor his baby Clemmie because she was
OL,16,Funable to run from the vehicle's path.
OL,18,FIn the incident, his wife was hit and
OL,19,Fhad to be pulled from underneath the
OL,20,Ftruck.
