OL,6,FMrs Bunford added that she initially
OL,7,Fthought her young son was safe after
OL,8,Fshe had pushed him from the vehicle,
OL,9,Fit was only when she looked over she
OL,10,Fsaw that he was injured.
OL,12,FEmergency services attended the
OL,13,Fincident and attempted to resuscitate
OL,14,FTomos.
OL,16,FMr Knox, the coroner, read statements
OL,17,Ffrom expert witnesses, who listed
OL,18,Ffactors that could have contributed to
OL,19,Fthe incident.
