OL,3,CBoy, 9, died after being struck by
OL,4,Cfarm vehicle in tragic accident
OL,6,FAn investigation by the Health and
OL,7,FSafety Executive found the braking
OL,8,Fmechanism on the trailer was
OL,9,Fdefective, meaning its towing capacity
OL,10,Fwas reduced to 750kg. It was carrying
OL,11,Fa load of 2,240kg.
OL,13,FThe investigator also found that the
OL,14,Ftyres on the Mitzubishi were
OL,15,Fmismatched and not suitable for off-
OL,16,Froad use, while the water bowser was
OL,17,Falso only three-quarters full, and the
OL,18,Fwater movement possibly added to the
OL,19,Fsteering issues.
