OL,6,FMr Knox recorded a conclusion of
OL,7,Faccidental death caused by blunt force
OL,8,Finjuries to the chest and abdomen.
OL,10,FThe assistant coroner expressed his
OL,11,Fdeepest condolences to the Bunford
OL,12,Ffamily for the "tragic loss of their
OL,13,Fson" and said that he will not be
OL,14,Fissuing a prevention of future deaths
OL,15,Forder in this case.
